    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Goblin Assault 是一款史诗级塔防冒险游戏，你将抵御无尽的哥布林、怪物和强大boss的进攻。锻造你的战略，准备迎接一场传奇之战！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301160/extras/2b572a33639ab65d4ef0bb8c38e79e50.webp?t=1772361167\" width=616 height=49 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301160/extras/40cf5a0d9927e6ae13570076744a1a08.poster.avif?t=1772361167\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301160/extras/40cf5a0d9927e6ae13570076744a1a08.webm?t=1772361167\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301160/extras/40cf5a0d9927e6ae13570076744a1a08.mp4?t=1772361167\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于 Goblin Assault</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Goblin Assault 是一款史诗级塔防游戏，你将防御来自哥布林、凶猛生物和决心摧毁你防线的强大boss的波次进攻。指挥强大的盟军单位，释放毁灭性的法术，升级塔防以守住阵线。每一波都带来新的挑战，要求快速思考和精准的战略。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301160/extras/434677872edc1823788bb13a948b0373.webp?t=1772361167\" width=616 height=49 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301160/extras/bdaf2be7395e305861af2a6e27d4b72d.poster.avif?t=1772361167\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301160/extras/bdaf2be7395e305861af2a6e27d4b72d.webm?t=1772361167\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301160/extras/bdaf2be7395e305861af2a6e27d4b72d.mp4?t=1772361167\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特色</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着进度的推进，解锁新的升级，迎战更致命的敌人，并征服充满激烈战斗的可重玩关卡。准备好你的防御，集结你的力量，成为这场生死存亡战斗中的终极指挥官！</p>",
